A+B\sim D_A+D_B?
A=D_A=D_B=\begin{pmatrix}1&0\\0&-1\end{pmatrix}
B=-A
 A = \begin{bmatrix}0&1\\1&0\end{bmatrix} \sim \begin{bmatrix}1&0\\0&-1\end{bmatrix} = D_{A}, 
 B = \begin{bmatrix}0&0\\0&1\end{bmatrix} = D_{B}. 
 A + B = \begin{bmatrix}0&1\\1&1\end{bmatrix} 
